# Technical stack

- Python for backend (Agents logic & Orchestration using   
  Langchain-LangGraph,CrewAI)
- Local LLM via Ollama API for natural langauge processing
- Flask/FastAPI for lightweight API services
- Alpaca or IEX Cloud API for real time stock data
- Numpy, Pandas for calculations and risk metrics
- Basic statistical libraries for risk management
- React, HTML or Javascript for frontend UI for the dashboard
- Socket.IO for real time updates
- Recharts/Charts.js for visualization
- PostgreSQL or SQLite for prototyping
- Git for Version Contrtol